---
title: BBQ Chicken Bulgogi with stir-fried veg and  jasmine rice
description: Bulgogi is a wildly popular type of Korean BBQ. Although the name literally translates as 'fire meat' this chicken bulgogi is only mildly spiced. Served with stir-fried mushrooms and onions as well as fragrant jasmine rice this recipe is perfect for all palates.
